                    <span>the book brings together two recently updated, important standards for (software) quality management: CMMI and ISO 9001.<br>the book is thoroughly set up and structured, easy to interpret and navigate with all the necessary mappings and tables, and<br>systematic considerations of process improvement approaches.<br>also of interest for people only focussing on the CMMI and not ISO. well done!</span>
                  
              
